cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.MM

This paper is about improving single-view depth estimation using neural networks. The most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision) since the paper deals with image processing and depth estimation. The second likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning) since the paper proposes a new type of convolution that can take camera parameters into account, which is a machine learning technique. The third likely category is cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) since the paper proposes a new technique for improving depth estimation using neural networks. The fourth likely category is cs.RO (Robotics) since depth estimation is an important task in robotics. The fifth likely category is cs.MM (Multimedia) since the paper deals with image processing and depth estimation, which are important topics in multimedia.
